reviewText: This was a mislabeled copy of "Shogun Assassin". It had the correct box and correct label on the DVD, but when I played it only "Shogun Assassin" would play. Pretty sure something illegal is going on here.
I have always been a believer of Kajukenbo martial arts. The first and original Mix Martial Arts. Nice to see one of the founder still doing this great art.

very cool video don't know much about kajukenbo but its looks like pretty awsome stuff to me it also has the founder of the style on the video how cool is that I heard he was an awsome fighter and a very smart man i think any kajukenbo student would enjoy this tape
